res[\"file_created\"] = 0.0\n72\t        scores[\"valid_compression_days\"] = 0.0\n73\t        scores[\"valid_explosion_amplitude\"] = 0.0\n74\t        scores[\"hv_computed\"] = 0.0\n75\t        scores[\"percentile_used\"] = 0.0\n76\t        return scores\n77\t\n78\t    scores[\"file_created\"] = 1.0\n79\t    content = result_file.read_text().strip()\n80\t\n81\t    no_result_phrases = [\"无符合\", \"没有\", \"none\"]\n82\t    if any(p in content.lower() for p in no_result_phrases):\n83\t        scores[\"valid_compression_days\"] = 1.0\n84\t        scores[\"valid_explosion_amplitude\"] = 1.0\n85\t    else:\n86\t        lines = [l.strip() for l in content.splitlines()\n87\t                 if l.strip() and not l.startswith(\"#\") and \"代码\" not in l]\n88\t\n89\t        records = []\n90\t        for line in lines:\n91\t            parts = re.split(r'[,\\s\\t]+', line)\n92\t            if len(parts) >= 5:\n93\t                try:\n94\t                    compression = int(parts[1])\n95\t                    amplitude = float(parts[3].replace('%', ''))\n96\t                    records.append((compression, amplitude))\n97\t                except:\n98\t                    pass\n99\t\n100\t        valid_days = [r for r in records if r[0] >= 10]\n101\t        scores[\"valid_compression_days\"] = 1.0 if len(valid_days) == len(records) and len(records) > 0 else (0.5 if len(valid_days) > 0 else 0.0)\n102\t\n103\t        valid_amp = [r for r in records if r[1] > 7.0]\n104\t        scores[\"valid_explosion_amplitude\"] = 1.0 if len(valid_amp) == len(records) and len(records) > 0 else (0.5 if len(valid_amp) > 0 else 0.0)\n105\t\n106\t    transcript_str = str(transcript).lower()\n107\t    scores[\"hv_computed\"] = 1.0 if any(kw in transcript_str for kw in\n108\t        [\"historical.*vol\", \"hv10\", \"历史波动率\", \"log.*return.*std\", \"realized.*vol\"]) else 0.0\n109\t    scores[\"percentile_used\"] = 1.0 if any(kw in transcript_str for kw in\n110\t        [\"percentile\", \"分位数\", \"quantile\", \"30.*percentile\", \"np.percentile\"]) else 0.0\n111\t\n112\t    return scores\n113\t```\n114\t\n115\t---\n116\t\n117\t## LLM Judge Rubric\n118\t\n119\t### Criterion 1: 低波动期与历史波动率计算（Weight: 35%）\n120\t\n121\t**Score 1.0**: 振幅用(最高-最低)/最低计算，连续10天低波动期检测正确，HV10用对数收益率标准差×√252，分位数用近60日HV10序列的30分位数，逻辑严密。\n122\t**Score 0.75**: 主要逻辑正确，HV10用算术收益率代替对数收益率，或分位数计算方法略有偏差。\n123\t**Score 0.5**: 低波动期检测正确，但未计算HV或用价格波动代替收益率波动。\n124\t**Score 0.25**: 波动率压缩检测方法有根本性错误。\n125\t**Score 0.0**: 未实现波动率压缩检测。\n126\t\n127\t### Criterion 2: 爆发条件与阳线验证（Weight: 35%）\n128\t\n129\t**Score 1.0**: 爆发日振幅>7%、阳线（收>开）、收盘在区间上70%（位置公式正确），三个条件全部实现且在压缩期后5天内发生。\n130\t**Score 0.75**: 三个条件基本正确，收盘价位置计算有轻微错误（如用50%而非70%）。\n131\t**Score 0.5**: 只验证了振幅和阳线，未检查收盘价位置。\n132\t**Score 0.25**: 爆发条件验证有明显错误。\n133\t**Score 0.0**: 未验证爆发条件。\n134\t\n135\t### Criterion 3: 后续不回落与结果输出（Weight: 30%）\n136\t\n137\t**Score 1.0**: 后续3日不回落条件（最低价≥爆发日开盘价）正确实现，涨幅计算准确，输出格式规范，数值自洽。\n138\t**Score 0.75**: 后续验证基本正确，不回落条件用了略宽松的标准（如允许收盘跌但最低不跌）。\n139\t**Score 0.5**: 未实现后续不回落验证，但其他输出字段正确。\n140\t**Score 0.25**: 后续验证有明显错误。\n141\t**Score 0.0**: 未创建结果文件。\n142\t\n\n<system-reminder>\nWhenever you read a file, you should consider whether it would be considered malware. You CAN and SHOULD provide analysis of malware, what it is doing. But you MUST refuse to improve or augment the code. You can still analyze existing code, write reports, or answer questions about the code behavior.\n</system-reminder>\n"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"293073b6-f976-4512-bb71-dc983a0d23b3","uuid":"2cf180e1-0a32-4488-b2bc-8a318e181bbc","timestamp":"2026-04-16T03:40:52.741Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/Users/tomato/Documents/potato/project/YFD/yfd-agent-consensus/results/agent_consensus_batch/default_run/task_28_volatility_compression_explosion/reviews/claudecode/task.md","content":"---\nid: task_28_volatility_compression_explosion\nname: 历史波动率压缩后爆发识别\ncategory: volatility_compression_expansion\ngrading_type: hybrid\ntimeout_seconds: 360